PoP and its accompanying balance changes is the literal realisation of the dreams of every Mage who has struggled through this far. At this point in time Magicians, and especially good ones are a very rare breed, its a very sad fact and hopefully that will change.<br>
<br>
I would like to extend a personal invitation to new Mages to begin posting ... I have started reading the &quot;who's online&quot; list when I come to the Tower and seeing a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>lot</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> of names I can't place as posting.<br>
